query:
INSERT INTO async_times (race_id, async_part, finish_time, recorded_by, link)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
            ON CONFLICT (race_id, async_part) DO UPDATE SET
                finish_time = EXCLUDED.finish_time,
                recorded_at = NOW(),
                recorded_by = EXCLUDED.recorded_by,
                link = EXCLUDED.link
